parcel.name: Portal Hub (MVB)
parcel.description:
This is the Portal Hub. It contains the Dirstrict Parcel Network, where you can travel to all the cryptovoxel districts and get back. The Portal Hub is also featuring ongoing events.

Visit https://www.metaverse-billboards.com for more info.

features.text: Disruption starts in the petri dish.
From there it will spread fast.
There is always a port back to this parcel!
